               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 5ra-80vb)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns (fols. 5ra-8va)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 8va-9vb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 9vb-10va)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 91 miracles (fols. 10va-80vb)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾƎsaggǝd laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām Mariham ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli ... "I worship Thee, O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..." (<locus from="7vb" to="8ra">7vb-8ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Māryām dǝngǝl ʾǝmma madḫǝn ǝmmä bǝrhān ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady, Virgin Mary, Mother of the Saviour, Mother of the Light ..." (<locus target="8ra">8ra-</locus>va).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>All miracles of Mary (Text I-4) are numbered. Miracles 21, 22 and 23 are followed by a poem:</note>
                     <note>- <locus target="30rb">30rb</locus>:</note>
                     <note>ዛካርያስ፡ ርእየ፡ በወርኃ፡ ሳባጥ፡ በሠርቁ።</note>
                     <note>ተአምረኪ፡ ለዘይት፡ ማዕከለ፡ ፪ኤ፡ አዕፁቁ።</note>
                     <note>ማርያም፡ ጽዮን፡ ለብርሃን፡ ተቅዋመ፡ ወርቁ።</note>
                     <note>ዕዝራኒ፡ በገዳም፡ አመ፡ ወዓለ፡ ውዱቁ።</note>
                     <note>ለኅብረ፡ ገጽኪ፡ ጽጌ፡ ሐተወ፡ መብረቁ።</note>
                     <note>(= a strophe from the Māḥleta ṣǝge "Canticle of the Flower", cp. GrohHymn p. 78).</note>
                     <note>- <locus target="31ra">31ra</locus>:</note>
                     <note>ታቦተ፡ አምላከ፡ ፳ኤል፡ ጽዮን፡ ማርያም፡ ዘነገደት፡ ምድረ፡ ኢሎፍሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወቀጥቀጠቶ፡ ለዳጎን፡ ነፍሳተ፡ ብዙሃን፡ ማኅጐሊ።</note>
                     <note>አመ፡ ነገደት፡ ቍስቋም፡ በኃይለ፡ ወልዳ፡ ከሃሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወድቁ፡ አማልክተ፡ ግብፅ፡ መናብርተ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ሀባሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወተኃፍሩ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ {ዘቦሙ፡} አስጋሊ።</note>
                     <note>- <locus target="31vb">31vb</locus>:</note>
                     <note>እስከ፡ መነነቶ፡ ሚልኮል፡ ቅድመ፡ ታቦተ፡ ሕግ፡ አመ፡ ዘፈነ።</note>
                     <note>ንጉሠ፡ ፳ኤል፡ ኪያኪ፡ ዘጸገየ፡ ስነ።</note>
                     <note>ቅድመ፡ ገጸ፡ ሥዕልኪ፡ እንዘ፡ እዘፍን፡ አነ።</note>
                     <note>ዘይሜንን፡ ተአምረኪ፡ ወሰብሐተኪ፡ ቍርባነ።</note>
                     <note>በአፈ፡ መላእክት፡ ወሰብእ፡ ለይኩን፡ ምኑነ።</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Text I-4 concludes with a supplication for the scribe.</note>
